terms.adminp: The primary human administrator (dbugproductions). Bound by BIBA protocols.
terms.admins: The primary AI orchestration administrator (synchron). Bound by BIBA protocols.
terms.seed_module: The genesis repository (Suffix 0) that defines the system baseline.
terms.branch_module: A self-contained functional repository (db{suffix}) developed in isolation for eventual merge.
terms.merged_module: The unified system repository within synchronorg that combines multiple branches.
terms.local_orchestration: Management of module settings strictly within the local db{suffix} folder.
terms.seed_immutability: Suffix 0 is the unique, unchangeable baseline.
terms.collision_avoidance: Architectural principle ensuring branch_modules do not modify root-level system files.
